{
  "stem": "1917.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I-- I-- [SOBBING] I think the children maybe-- I don't know at what age it starts-- but I would say all children who are faced with life and death situations are no longer children.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I just pushed the dolls inside, and I never wanted to look at them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We stayed there for a few months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there were many things I didn't like about the monastery.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I didn't feel very comfortable in a Catholic monastery with-- they didn't try to convert us or anything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was run by the Red Cross and by the Jewish Joint.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The nice thing was that we could leave any time and come back as we pleased.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We would show our numbers, and we would get on the street car, one that ran by, and travel the-- one end of town to the other.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was great fun.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we found out somehow that, at one edge of town, there was a refugee camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we wanted to find Mrs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Csengeri.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Because I knew that she survived with her two twin daughters-- and wanted her to come and sign some papers, so we could go with her.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I could have walked away, but I didn't know where to go by myself in the big world.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I was just-- just-- tooks-- I wanted to go home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "That's all I wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And so she came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And she took care of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we stayed with her all the way until we got home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- there-- people were grouped in these refugees camps, or DP camps-- were grouped according to country of origin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in a camp in Katowice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then from there, we were taken to a camp in Czernowitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
